{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/removeannotation:"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"- ("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"removeAnnotation:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"id<MLNAnnotation>","preciseIdentifier":"c:Qoobjc(pl)MLNAnnotation"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"annotation"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"parameters":[{"name":"annotation","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The annotation object to remove. This object must conform","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to the ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" protocol","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Removing an annotation object dissociates it from the map view entirely,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"preventing it from being displayed on the map. Thus you would typically call"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"this method only when you want to hide or delete a given annotation."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/removeAnnotation:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Removes an annotation from the map view, deselecting it if it is selected."}],"sections":[],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Instance Method","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(im)removeAnnotation:","title":"removeAnnotation:","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"removeAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"removeAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"}],"remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L1820","fileName":"MLNMapView.h"},"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"symbolKind":"method"},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects to handle the display."}],"title":"MLNAnnotation","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","title":"MapLibre","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","kind":"symbol","role":"collection"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView/removeAnnotation:":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/removeannotation:","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Removes an annotation from the map view, deselecting it if it is selected."}],"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"removeAnnotation:"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/removeAnnotation:","role":"symbol","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"removeAnnotation:"}],"title":"removeAnnotation:"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView":{"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMapView"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","kind":"symbol","title":"MLNMapView","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An interactive, customizable map view with an interface similar to the one"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provided by Apple’s MapKit."}],"type":"topic","role":"symbol"}}}